    <note>Chen(1) Jue [29] His grandson, Xian [3066], entered the civil service via his yin of Jue, followed by success in a decree exam and rose to a position as Hubu shilang in 1179. Zhenjiang TZ, 124.22a has him as a 1112 jinshi, whereas other souirces have him earning a university degree in this year. I am assuming that from the university he earned the jinshi. Zhen Dexiu, WJ, 44.1a-6a; XNYL, 86.13b, 101.6a, 166.12b, 193.6a, 195.6b; Xianchun Linan zhi, 50.8a; SHY:SH, 56.60b; Shengzheng, 57.3b; SS, 377.14b, 15a. CBD, 3, 2475-6.</note>
